org.cloudsimplus.listeners

Interface EventInfo

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    DatacenterEventInfo, HostEventInfo, SimEvent, VmEventInfo
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CloudletEventInfoSimple, CloudSimEvent, DatacenterToVmEventInfo, EventInfoSimple, HostEventInfoSimple, HostToVmEventInfo, HostUpdatesVmsProcessingEventInfo, VmEventInfoSimple, VmToCloudletEventInfo

    public interface EventInfo
    An interface which defines the basic methods that an object representing data about a happened event must have. Classes implementing this interface are to pass information about an happened event to an EventListener object.
    Since:
    CloudSim Plus 1.0
    Author:
    Manoel Campos da Silva Filho
